    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, mint-condition car that has clearly been very well cared for. It shows beautifully inside and out, feels fresh and tight on the road, and has the kind of overall presentation that\u2019s hard to find. A standout example for someone looking for a truly well-kept car.",
