    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept older vehicle in good overall condition. It presents nicely for its age and should make a solid daily driver or weekend car for someone looking for a usable, respectable example rather than a showpiece. Expect normal age-related cosmetic wear and some minor imperfections inside and out, but nothing out of line for an older vehicle in this condition. Overall, this is a straightforward, honest car that appears to have been maintained reasonably well and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
