      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "Fair-condition car that runs and drives, but it shows clear wear inside and out consistent with age and use. Expect cosmetic imperfections and some overall signs of being less well-kept than a clean example. Not a perfect car, but it could be a reasonable option for someone looking for a lower-priced driver.",
      "price": 18900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Opportunity-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable daily transportation. It shows the wear you would expect from a well-used car, but it still presents strong value for a buyer who wants practical mobility without a big upfront cost. A smart option for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone looking for a budget-friendly runabout with room to make it their own.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it starts, runs, and could make a great cheap runabout, project, or spare vehicle for someone handy. Priced to reflect its condition, and I\u2019m happy to answer questions so you know exactly what you\u2019re getting.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with good bones and plenty of usable life left. It shows cosmetic wear consistent with age, but the powertrain pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and it remains a practical driver or ideal project platform. A straightforward, no-nonsense option for someone who wants affordable transportation with mechanical potential instead of paying a premium for cosmetics. Priced to move and worth a look if you know what matters.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Honest used shape, priced to move fast.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, lived-in personality you notice right away\u2014a machine with stories behind it and plenty of road still ahead for the right owner. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership for someone who values charm, utility, and the satisfaction of bringing out a vehicle\u2019s next chapter. Whether you need a budget-friendly runabout, a hands-on project, or a practical spare to keep around, this one offers real potential wrapped in unmistakable character.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for someone looking for affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. Offered in openly advertised poor condition, it presents a chance to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price point. A sensible choice for a value-minded buyer who appreciates transparency and potential.",
      "price": 4995.0,
